entry.title: jbromley/brownian
entry.summary:
Simple Brownian motion simulation.

Brownian

This project is a simple simulation of random motion. The user adds particles with the mouse buttons and can adjust the size and speed of new particles. This is meant as a benchmark to compare a Common Lisp/SDL game with versions in other languages.
